name: My Business Presence
tag_list: social-media, blogging, implementation, search-engine-optimization, workshop, public-speaking, training, entrepreneur, small-business, sales
overview:
My Business Presence offers practical presentations, fun and effective workshops, and ethical online marketing for small business owners who want to increase their online presence through a website, social media, blogging and knowledge of search engine optimization.

We use our 11+ years experience marketing a product online to teach others how to get started. We meet them where they are to make learning about internet marketing fun and effective.

People we work with attend or host classes with their peers who bring their own laptops while we are there for hands-on instruction and guidance. We also offer online presence evaluations, which can be a great starting point in finding out where to spend your time improving your presence online. Some of the other services we provide are social media and event listing implementation, speaking to groups, private tutoring in your home or office, and telephone or email consultation.
